<div ng-app="post_sale" >
<div ng-controller="firstController">
<div class="container bg-2 text-center" >
  <div>     
  <h4 class="margin">
  <label for="sel1">Number of Items</label>
      <select  ng-model="selectedName" class="form-control" ng-options="item for item in numbers" id="num_items"></select>      
    </h4>
   </div>
    <h4>
    <div class="form-group has-success has-feedback">
      <label for="inputSuccess2">Sale Location</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sale_loc" ng-model="sale_loc">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok form-control-feedback"></span>
    </div>
    </h4>
    <h4>
    <div class="form-group has-success has-feedback">
      <label for="inputSuccess2">Sale Date</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sale_date" ng-model="sale_date">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok form-control-feedback"></span>
    </div>
    </h4>
  <p>Slect Number of Items that you want to sale in this sale, After selecting number of items click 'Go..Sale..' it will display place to give your order details. After Everything is set to go, yes go sale your items. 
    Note: Max number of Items you can sell in a sale is 9, if you want to sale more items go ahead and create new sale (just for catchy of sale ) </p>
  <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg padding_down"  ng-click="show_below_grid('AngularJS')" id='go_sale'>
    <span class="glyphicon"></span> Go..Sale..
  </a>
</div>
<div>
<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide container" data-ride="carousel" ng-show="display_corosal">
    <!-- Indicators -->
    <ol class="carousel-indicators" id="coro_indi">
    </ol>
    <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox" id="item_details">
        <div class='item active'><form action='' method='post' enctype='multipart/form-data'>
             <center>
                <section id='create' style='margin-top:23px;position:relative;color:black;width:80%;'>	
                   <table class='table table-bordered'>
                      <tr>
                             <td colspan='2' style='text-align:center'>
                       <h3>Item -1 </h3></td></tr>
                       <tr>
                       <td>Item Category:</td>
                        <td><select class="form-control" ng-options="item for item in category" id="num_items" ng-model='item.category'></select>
                           </td>
                       </tr>
                      <tr>
                       <td>Item Name:</td>
                          <td><input type='text' placeholder='Item name' class='form-control' name='title' id='eventname' ng-model='item.name'/></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                      <td>Item Description:</td>
                          <td><textarea placeholder='Description' class='form-control' id='descr' ng-model='item.descr'></textarea></td>
                      </tr>
                       
                      <tr>
                          <td>Photos:</td>
                      <td>
                              
                              <span class=''>
                              <input type='file' multiple placeholder='Multiple Selection allowed' accept="image/*" id='item_photos' ng-model='item.photos'>
                              </span>
                      </td>
                      </tr>
                       <td> 
                           Item Condition:
                       </td>
                       <td>
                           <form role="form">
                                 <label class="radio-inline">
                                 <input type="radio" name="condition" ng-model='item.condition' value="used" checked>Used
                                 </label>
                                 <label class="radio-inline">
                                 <input type="radio" name="condition" ng-model='item.condition' value="new" >New
                                 </label>
                           </form>
                       </td>
                       <tr>
                             <td>
                                  Price 
                             </td>
                             <td>
                                 <form role="form">
                                 <label class="radio-inline">
                                 <input type="radio" name="price_free" ng-model='item.price_free' value=false ng-click="show_hide_price(false)" checked>Free
                                 </label>
                                 <label class="radio-inline">
                                 <input type="radio" name="price_free" ng-model='item.price_free' value=true ng-click="show_hide_price(true)">Sale
                                 </label>
                                 </form>
                             </td> 
                       </tr>
                       <tr id="price_item">
                           <td>
                           </td>
                               <td>
                                      <input type="text" placeholder="enter price" ng-model='item.price'/>
                                  </td>
                       </tr>
                       <tr>
                           <td>
                               Quantity:
                           </td>
                           <td>
                               <input type="number" min="0" ng-model='item.qty'/>
                           </td>
                       </tr>
                              
        </table>
    </section>
    </center>
    </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div colspan="3" style="text-align:center">
     <input type="button" id="register" value="Post Sale" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color:#1B7B98" ng-click='add_image_grid()'/>
    </div>
     
    <!-- Left and right controls -->
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>